rows.label: qst650412_msg0001
rows.name: Oh dear. That child seems troubled...

rows.label: qst650412_msg0002
rows.name: We should see what the matter is.

rows.label: qst650412_msg0003
rows.name:
Hey there, little one.
What's the matter?

rows.label: qst650412_msg0004
rows.name:
My mum and dad went out somewhere and
they've been gone a long time...

rows.label: qst650412_msg0005
rows.name: And now you're hungry and upset?

rows.label: qst650412_msg0006
rows.name: How did you know...?

rows.label: qst650412_msg0007
rows.name: Oh, you know...I'm just kind like that!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0008
rows.name:
If you've got some ingredients
at home, we can try and make
you something! How about it?

rows.label: qst650412_msg0009
rows.name: Really?!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0010
rows.name: Of course!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0011
rows.name:
Just you watch, Homura! I'll make
him a meal he won't soon forget!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0012
rows.name: O-Okay... Give it your best, Hibana!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]It buuuuuuuuuuuuurns!!!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0201
rows.name: A most unfortunate outcome, Hibana.

rows.label: qst650412_msg0202
rows.name:
It looks like I'm not quite on
Homura's level just yet...

rows.label: qst650412_msg0203
rows.name:
I must've put too much
fire into the dish and it
got a bit...explosive...

rows.label: qst650412_msg0204
rows.name:
I personally thought it
was quite all right...

rows.label: qst650412_msg0205
rows.name:
A child's taste buds are more
sensitive, though. You do have
to take that into account.

rows.label: qst650412_msg0206
rows.name: I guess I should have...

rows.label: qst650412_msg0207
rows.name:
Well, no matter. Next time
will be a success, I know it!

rows.label: qst650412_msg0208
rows.name: I believe in you, Hibana.

rows.label: qst650412_msg0209
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Thanks, that means so much to me!
I'll make you proud, Homura!
